  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/fbf88d80cfe9ef5f5f4ca0c7c5c65f00.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=104 /></span><br><br><strong>1 Bit Survivor</strong> is an easy to play but difficult to master randomly generated rogue-like with stylized pixel art and survival horror elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.poster.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.webm?t=1691761173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.mp4?t=1691761173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Simple controls</strong>: Move and Shoot<br></li><li> <strong>Survival Horror</strong>: Limited resources make every decision matter<br></li><li> <strong>Turn-Based</strong>: Take your time and make your choices carefully<br></li><li> <strong>Rogue-like</strong>: Only one chance to survive, if you die it is Game Over<br></li><li> <strong>Upgrade</strong> your character with <strong>randomized Items</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Choose</strong> your play style with three <strong>Unlockable Classes</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Compete </strong>for the fastest time in the <strong>Online Leaderboards</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/1ca104303710cd31fa5aa440e13d7243.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=104 /></span><br>The world has been lost to a <strong>deadly virus</strong>, transforming the citizens into <i>flesh eating mutants</i>. <br><br>In <strong>28 Days</strong> the military plans to <i>nuke everything</i> above ground in a last ditch effort to gain control. Unfortunately for you, the nearest bunker is <i>very far away</i>.<br><br>Will you <strong>fight</strong> your way to safety, or <i>succumb</i> to the Zed-pocalypse?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/fbf88d80cfe9ef5f5f4ca0c7c5c65f00.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=104 /></span><br><br><strong>1 Bit Survivor</strong> is an easy to play but difficult to master randomly generated rogue-like with stylized pixel art and survival horror elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.poster.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.webm?t=1691761173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/79335a0944623a447d824623c1d45f4c.mp4?t=1691761173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Simple controls</strong>: Move and Shoot<br></li><li> <strong>Survival Horror</strong>: Limited resources make every decision matter<br></li><li> <strong>Turn-Based</strong>: Take your time and make your choices carefully<br></li><li> <strong>Rogue-like</strong>: Only one chance to survive, if you die it is Game Over<br></li><li> <strong>Upgrade</strong> your character with <strong>randomized Items</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Choose</strong> your play style with three <strong>Unlockable Classes</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Compete </strong>for the fastest time in the <strong>Online Leaderboards</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493160/extras/1ca104303710cd31fa5aa440e13d7243.avif?t=1691761173\" width=600 height=104 /></span><br>The world has been lost to a <strong>deadly virus</strong>, transforming t